@startuml Order Processing Saga - Payment Failure
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Saga-хореография оформления заказа - Ошибка оплаты

actor "Покупатель" as Customer
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Event Bus" as EventBus
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Payment Gateway" as PaymentGW
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Order History Service" as History

Customer -> Order: Оформить заказ
activate Order
Order -> Order: Создать заказ\n(статус: CREATED)
Order -> EventBus: Publish: OrderCreated
deactivate Order

EventBus -> Inventory: OrderCreated
activate Inventory
Inventory -> Inventory: Проверить наличие товаров
Inventory -> Inventory: Зарезервировать товары
Inventory -> EventBus: Publish: InventoryReserved
deactivate Inventory

EventBus -> Payment: InventoryReserved
activate Payment
Payment -> PaymentGW: Запрос на оплату
activate PaymentGW
PaymentGW --> Payment: Ошибка оплаты\n(недостаточно средств)
deactivate PaymentGW
Payment -> Payment: Сохранить неудачную\nтранзакцию
Payment -> EventBus: Publish: PaymentFailed
note right
  Причина: недостаточно средств,
  неверные данные карты,
  лимит превышен
end note
deactivate Payment

EventBus -> Inventory: PaymentFailed
activate Inventory
Inventory -> Inventory: Освободить зарезервированные\nтовары
Inventory -> EventBus: Publish: InventoryReleased
deactivate Inventory

EventBus -> Order: PaymentFailed
activate Order
Order -> Order: Отменить заказ\n(статус: CANCELLED)
Order -> EventBus: Publish: OrderCancelled
deactivate Order

EventBus -> History: OrderCreated,\nInventoryReserved,\nPaymentFailed,\nInventoryReleased,\nOrderCancelled
activate History
History -> History: Обновить историю заказа
History -> EventBus: Publish: OrderStatusUpdated\n(статус: CANCELLED)
deactivate History

EventBus -> Notification: OrderCancelled
activate Notification
Notification ->> Customer: Отправить уведомление\n(заказ отменен:\nошибка оплаты)
Notification -> EventBus: Publish: CustomerNotificationSent
deactivate Notification

Customer -> Order: Проверить статус заказа
activate Order
Order --> Customer: Статус: CANCELLED\nПричина: ошибка оплаты
deactivate Order

@enduml
